nodes.text: A group of red-eyed quadruped creatures lived in the streets of an industrial city at some point during the reign of the New Republic. The street lights seemed to repel them, so they tended to stay in the shadows.

After an altercation stemming from a disagreement in a fighting arena around 9 ABY, the Mandalorian Din Djarin brought Gor Koresh outside and subdued him, hanging him upside-down from a streetlight pole and forcing information out of him. Djarin then shot the bulb out, leaving Koresh at the mercy of these creatures.
